channel.title: Intdubpk.no-ip.biz source, client help!
channel.description:
A guy who also had this problem was told to change "intdubpk.no-ip.biz" to his IP or 127.0.0.1 in the Gui.java and client.java. I have done this, but it still comes up with the same error. I have also edited the run.bat to my JDK. "Run server" works fine, just the client I'm struggling with. Please help? item.title: Intdubpk.no-ip.biz source, client help!
item.dc:creator: @ultimatepkvillage ultimatepkvillage
item.description:
@ultimatepkvillage wrote:

that error is telling you that it cannot recognized Intdubpk.no-ip.biz

search in client.java and gui.java and use Ctrl H in the find box put Intdubpk.no-ip.biz and Replace with box put 127.0.0.1 then click the replace all button

then compile
